Be informed, ITHM Tamaraws!  

Pubmat by: Alexi Margarette Montecastro

Reference: https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1F6jZ9Zqi5/?mibextid=wwXIfr

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
